* [[citronowy bom]]<ref>{{dnw|titel= Zitronenbaum}}</ref> (''Citrus limon'')
* [[citronatowa citrona]] (''Citrus medica'')
* [[grapefruit]]<ref>{{starosta1999|bok=149}}</ref><ref>{{dnw|titel= Grapefruit}}</ref> (''Citrus x paradisi'')
